sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant S as /diagram skill
  participant T as diagram.sh
  participant M as npx mmdc
  participant C as system Chrome
  U->>S: /diagram "flowchart..."
  S->>T: invoke
  T->>T: structural validate (.mmd)
  alt Chrome present
    T->>M: render via puppeteer cfg
    M->>C: headless render
    C-->>T: SVG
    T-->>U: status=ok (tracked asset + source)
  else Chrome absent
    T-->>U: status=unavailable (source kept, hint)
  end
